posts.subject: Invictus' Platform
posts.body:
RESTORE THE NATURAL ORDER
We will revive the old ways, reinstating natural law as the highest law, recognizing concepts of marriage, gender, race, and the environment in the ancient sense.

DEFEND THE WEST
We will fight to preserve our proud heritage and educate our children in European High Culture, recognizing as total enemies all who undermine the Imperium.

END WHITE GENOCIDE
We will halt the flood of immigrants, cease all so-called diversity programs, and terminate the trend of Whites becoming unwelcome minorities in their own countries.

MAKE AMERICANS GREAT AGAIN
We will raise up the poor and working class by eschewing obsolete notions of capitalism and socialism, returning to a holistic nationalism.

BETTER DEAD THAN RED
We will crush the communist mob, curing the Marxist plague by physically removing the politicians, media executives, and professors instrumental in the epidemic.

STOP THE MACHINES
We will bring Silicon Valley to heel, implement farming & environmental initiatives to benefit the public welfare, and pursue policies that place humanity over technology.

DISMANTLE THE DEEP STATE
We will root out the corruption of the Federal Government, dissolving unnecessary bureaucratic institutions and trying traitors for treason.

EAT THE BANKERS
We will end the Federal Reserve and the power of the international banking cartels, prohibiting usury and ensuring that monetary policy is determined by the public interest.

CONQUER
We will wage war only in Americaâ€™s interests, never the interests of Israel, international finance, or the corrupt international order.
If the cylinder is arranged parallel to the page with the north pole on top of the page, the south on the bottom, and the electron flies in from the left, then it will deviate out of the page.
